1.	To Get Business Object Name:
var PM = SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetPModel();
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetBusObj().GetName();
2.	To Get Business Component Name:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetName();
3.	To Get list of field displayed in Business Component:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetFieldMap();
4.	To Get Business Component field value:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetFieldValue("BC_FIELD_NAME");
5.	To Get the current record BC Row Id value:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetIdValue();
6.	To Get a total number of rows displayed in the list applet:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetNumRows();
7.	To Get the current selected row from list applet:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetCurRowNum(); 
8.	To Get the current selected row from list applet:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetSelection(); 
9.	To Get the field name currently used for Sorting with ASC/DEC:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetSortSpec();
10.	To Get the Parent Business Component Name:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetParentBusComp().GetName();
11.	To Get the list of field displayed in Parent Business Component:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetParentBusComp().GetFieldMap();
12.	To Get the Parent Business Component field value:
PM.Get("GetBusComp").GetParentBusComp().GetFieldValue("BC_FIELD_NAME");
13.	To Get Siebel Application Name:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetAppTitle()
14.	To Get Siebel Application URL:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetPageURL()
15.	To Get/Set Profile Attribute:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetProfileAttr("ProfileAttr_Name")
SiebelApp.S_App.SetProfileAttr("ProfileAttr_Name","Value")
16.	To Log off the Siebel Application:
SiebelApp.S_App.LogOff()
17.	To Get Presentation Model instance:
var PM =SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetPModel()
18.	To Execute current Applet Method:
PM.ExecuteMethod("InvokeMethod","MethodName")
19.	To Get the status of Method availability:
PM.ExecuteMethod("CanInvokeMethod","MethodName")
20.	To Check whether user can update the control value:
PM.ExecuteMethod("CanUpdate","ControlName")
21.	To Check whether Control has Drilldown:
PM.ExecuteMethod("CanNavigate","ControlName")
22.	To Get the List of control present in the current applet:
PM.Get("GetControls")
23.	To Check whether applet has valid BC:
PM.Get("IsPure")
24.	To Check whether applet is in Query Mode:
PM.Get("IsInQueryMode")
25.	To Get Active View Name:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetName()
26.	To Get List Applet from Active View:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetAppletMap()
27.	To Get Active Applet Name:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetName()
28.	To Get Active Applet Mode:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetMode()
29.	To Invoke an Method from Active Applet:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().InvokeMethod("METHOD_NAME")
30.	To Get Active Business Object Name:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveBusObj().GetName()
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetBusObj().GetName()
31.	To Get Active Business Component Name:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetBusComp().GetName()
32.	To Get Field Value by providing Business Component & Field Name:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveBusObj().GetBusCompByName('BC_NAME').GetFieldValue('FIELD_NAME')
33.	To Check whether the record is unsaved in Active Applet:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetBusComp().IsCommitPending()
34.	To Get Number Record from Active List Applet:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetPModel().GetRenderer().GetGrid().getGridParam("reccount")
35.	To Hide/Show List Applet Control by it's Name:
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetPModel().GetRenderer().GetGrid().hideCol('LIST_CONTROL_NAME')
SiebelApp.S_App.GetActiveView().GetActiveApplet().GetPModel().GetRenderer().GetGrid().showCol('LIST_CONTROL_NAME')
36.	To Remove never ending busy icon:
SiebelApp.S_App.uiStatus.Free()

